Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大家都為保衛藍色的地球而拚命著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟快過年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(本集在96年12月31日播出)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就休假了…就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，是總集篇啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"機動戰艦"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍著痛苦所踢起的小石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若反彈回來也會變成鑽石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上到手的夢想不算是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是請堅信它一定會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡從不氣餒的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.02,0:01:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想哭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠永遠在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的方式驕傲地去面對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去熱衷的日子是夢的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那碎片收集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能看見以明天為目標的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOING YOUR DAY'S GROW UP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"激鋼人3"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想呼喚著明日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂的呼喚LET'S GO PASSION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天將和平用這隻手取回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GO 激鋼人-3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像"熱血卡通"般去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的撫子是特別節目嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是像介紹篇一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事也進行到轉涙點了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以需要一集用來整理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真清楚啊，純平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是因為製作公司面臨除夕忙不過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去，丈真現實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"撫子放送"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"撫子的為什麼"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快點集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是撫子的秘密時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天特別告訴你有關撫子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我來說明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2195年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球面臨最大的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體疏散!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以本艦撞擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的無人兵器軍團攻擊並佔領火星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更攻下了月球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至逼近地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球聯合軍也似乎毫無辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此這就輪到撫子出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NERGAL重工獨自開發機動戰艦撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形式NERGAL ND-001
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全長298M
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全高106.8M
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全幅148M，總重量37530磅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容人員2l4名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備四座核脈衝引擎兩座相轉移引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中樞電腦使用SVC2027思兼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本配備大概是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請先從位於十二層甲板最上方的艦橋看起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的指令都是從這兒發出的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，今天是假日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦橋的正下方就是虛擬實境室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來說明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間是為了要紓解乘員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長期處在宇宙空間的精神壓力而設置的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自動測量各自的腦波還有其他資料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行精神分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後創造出適合那個人的劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡設定明人是和我同一個社團的學長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放輕鬆放輕鬆…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼緊張的話沒辦法紓解壓力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是為了學長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為也有想在日常生活中除去煩惱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也有個冥想室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第四甲板有娛樂室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連2l96年型最新式桌球檯也有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有，隔壁有利用雷射投影的展望台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的風景，氣壓，氧氣濃度可以自由選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那下方的廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷梅今天也在發揮她的手藝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是年底或過年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說讓客人滿意也是做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們非得認真地加油不可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這不是在做生意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我自認手藝不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是職業的，完全不能比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球看似狹小，其實很廣大的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每塊土地都有那塊土地的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是我在臭蓋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店撫子食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有地球三百個地方的調味料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣，厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅茶葉也搜集了最上等的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠再放點酒那就更好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督，不可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要推薦料理的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是放了一堆章魚熱狗的火星井吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我個人比較喜歡雞肉飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不談那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們撫子最驕傲的人型機械人AESTIVALIS的機庫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排排站的AESTIVALIS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小AESTI真的事情就交．給．我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從陸戰模組開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎 這個直拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳躍力也出類拔萃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的空戰模組
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還更厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子的事交給我凱大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄就是得像這樣才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有，看看這架勢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何能在空中飛就已經帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田，你不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後必勝絕技是眾所皆知的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱，超級鉤拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒這麼沸騰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外這AESTIVALIS還有隱藏的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CROSS CRASH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣世界的和平就安全啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搞什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重裝模組的話我和明人一起坐過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種重量感真叫人受不了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C戰模組全部配備了四架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要駕駛員是天河明人，昴涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野光，真木泉這四人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧，十架才打中三架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來蚱蜢君的力場好像被強化了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會進化的機器?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近身戰是我的本行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，天河怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候來救我們的是最新型的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，是什麼，這個模組
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新型的啊，喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動機也很小巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連肌膚也滑溜溜地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就搞一輩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個以飛行員身份加入的赤月流行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及愛莉娜．金城．王\N這兩人，好像有什麼隱情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份，目的一切不明的無人兵器群
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類將這初次遭遇的異星文明稱為木星蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用入射角就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"激鋼射擊"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之至今的經歷是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有辦法對迅速進化的木星兵器施以重擊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡通真好啊，充滿夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是寫實的戰鬥場面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來會怎麼樣發展呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了，阿卡拉王子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然無法征服地球嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我正在收集有關地球人文化的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以便擬定作戰計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人的資料，有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我靜候佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料部份就差不多這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟2l4人同吃同住會有各式各樣的事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各式各樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長和天河明人君之間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉，真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼地方受傷了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來艦長跟天河君是青梅竹馬的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾經在哪裡見過面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，見過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，你肚子痛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了，走開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你一個提起精神的訣竅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼晴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，妳突然做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 居然在我不清楚的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明平常忙起來時都是我代理百合香工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了，冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊…年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這兩個看來真是很速配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了什麼才來火星的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從上了撫子之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是你第一次對我這麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜，要振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，你可以…吻我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香，妳在胡說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，只要你吻我 我會再加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會比現在更稍微賣力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人喜歡我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人有各種複雜的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，琉璃琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:14:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當大人也有很多好事唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你戴兔子帽很適合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的真是的，有各式各樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有"好事"嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們煩死了，給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河天河天河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載滿各種想法前進的機動戰艦撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後又將去哪裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人相戀的命運又會如何呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，真希望我能跟阿卡拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，阿卡拉大人看起來好像對我沒興趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有搜集到關於地球人文化的情報了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部叫"機動戰艦撫子"的卡通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為是調查地球人用的最好的樣本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡通是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把故事用圖來表現印地球人的娛樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，虛構故事這些脫離現實的東西真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊，天河
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人也有男人跟女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰鬥中萌芽的淡淡的戀情真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼愛呀戀情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這種事就能夠打贏嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下等的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個是什麼，米耶米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據資料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是叫做次元歪曲防壁的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種利用護罩進行的敵陣突破攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠反作用力突破敵陣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到可以在這種地方發現打敗激鋼人的秘策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好，米耶米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您的誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡拉大人專用機大阿卡拉SPECIAL待命出動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼人你等著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的飛行物體正急速接近研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張開護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做也沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元歪曲防壁!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地震嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍，丈，明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是機械怪獸的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們立刻出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，激鋼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出來的話我要下殺手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GEKIGER IN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼光束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西對我沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼劍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電漿斷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種玩具般的東西破不了這次元歪曲防壁的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧，激鋼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸，這樣下去會打輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈，最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然才剛完成還未測試
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這地步只好一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍，丈，明，用激鋼爆炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼爆炎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我為了防範於未然秘密開發的激鋼爆炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果沒有一氣呵成激鋼人會爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣的話也只能幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼爆炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個光芒是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡拉大人 請快點逃 阿卡拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，地球人給我記著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 博士 你什麼時候想出那種武器的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陣子在撫子裡演的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 博士也在看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了，快點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年夜麵正等著你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵，也有年糕嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是明天才吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"完"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎?這種結束方式?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此 下集也請繼續收看…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:21:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有純粹的情感沈睡其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要追尋夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容與淚水的數目就會漸漸增多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時想要更像自我地去感受風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不屬於其他人的我自己的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去發掘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是御統百合香的配音員 桑島法子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然低溫每天持續著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀賞機動戰艦撫子的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把冷風什麼的用次元歪曲防壁吹散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:22:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著次回木星蜥蜴的真面目似乎終於明瞭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼樣的故事呢? 我現在就好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香還有出場嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，次回機動戰艦撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"遙遠星球來的男友"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼說定囉
